%!PS

%	This example appears in section "Arcs Greater Than 360 Degrees"
%	in Chapter 7 - "Arcs and Curves".
%

/inch { 72 mul } def		%  define inch procedure
4.25 inch 5.5	inch		%  coordinates of center
3.0 inch			%  radius
0 405 arc			%  draw more than circle
0.5 inch setlinewidth		%  fat line width
stroke				%  paint outline
showpage			%  display page
